Earlier in the day, the Nigerian Instagram and Twitter space was taken by surprise by the accusation and counter-accusation of an anonymous social media user who it seems knows the intricate details of the celebrated house bought by Nigerian actress, Mercy Aigbe. According to a letter, Mercy Aigbe’s house was bought by a governor who many have alleged is Governor Ambode of Lagos state. The script allegedly mentions OAP Toke Makinwa as one of the beneficiaries of a house by the same governor. Read More: Nigerians React To Mercy Aigbe’s House Scandal See the story making rounds on the internet <img class="aligncenter wp-image-759467 lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mercy-aigbe-mansion.png" alt="" width="1000" height="914" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mercy-aigbe-mansion.png 593w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mercy-aigbe-mansion-487x445.png 487w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mercy-aigbe-mansion-263x240.png 263w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mercy-aigbe-mansion-525x480.png 525w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /> <img class="aligncenter wp-image-759466 lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mercy-aigbe-mansion-1-564x598.png" alt="" width="1000" height="1061" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mercy-aigbe-mansion-1-564x598.png 564w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mercy-aigbe-mansion-1-487x517.png 487w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mercy-aigbe-mansion-1-226x240.png 226w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mercy-aigbe-mansion-1-452x480.png 452w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mercy-aigbe-mansion-1-565x600.png 565w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/mercy-aigbe-mansion-1.png 573w" sizes="(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px" /> Aigbe has now responded to the allegation: Dear Bloggers, the mumu upcoming script writer! and association of instablog bad be